This paper involves machine learning techniques to solve the AC optimal power flow problem, which is a problem in power systems engineering. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also involves developing a mapping between system loading and optimal generation values, which involves machine learning techniques such as regression. Therefore, it is also likely to belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves optimization techniques, which could place it in categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves developing an online method, which could place it in cs.SE (Software Engineering).
